		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Plagiarizing is putting your name on someone else's work, thus falsely claiming that you created it. It'd be like someone posting foobar's NES test ROMs even though they were the ones I wrote. That's totally different from foobar's emulator including unmodified copies of blargg's NES test ROMs along with it.

		

